	<header class="entry-header">
		<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://joineverest.org/teenage-prodigies-arent-limited-to-glamour-sports" rel="bookmark">Teenage prodigies aren&#8217;t limited to glamour sports</a></h1>		
				<div class="entry-meta">
			<span class="posted-on"><a href="http://joineverest.org/teenage-prodigies-arent-limited-to-glamour-sports" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published" datetime="2015-08-11T04:24:07+00:00">August 11, 2015</time><time class="updated" datetime="2016-02-17T04:24:43+00:00">February 17, 2016</time></a></span><span class="byline"> - <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://joineverest.org/author/adm1n">mimin</a></span></span>						<span class="comments-link"><a href="http://joineverest.org/teenage-prodigies-arent-limited-to-glamour-sports#respond">Leave a comment</a></span>
